<p>The challenge was to solve some pain points of their <em>Hudl Technique</em> mobile app.</p>

<blockquote>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <p>Once a user has a number of videos in their library, managing those videos could be better.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Finding a specific video is difficult. For instance, if youâ€™re looking for a golf swing from two weeks ago, you might be scrolling through lots of video to find that specific one.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Thereâ€™s no notion of separating videos into groups or teams.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>

